<p>
  <span class="nym">Bona</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>bona</i> 'good, kind, right, pleasant; valid, useful, healthy'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 12th C Italian saint and a 15th C duchess of Savoy.</p>
</div>
  
  


